data.text:
Kevin "Wilson" Jon Schelander, 56, of Pequot Lakes passed away peacefully of February 10,2022 after a long battle with cancer. He was surrounded by his family at his home.

Kevin was born on June 7, 1965, to Dennis and Karen (Rudin) Schelander in Stillwater, Minnesota.

Kevin moved to Pequot Lakes in 2002 and founded his business of Schelander and Sons Construction.

Kevin is survived by sons, Austin (Katie) Schelander, Luke Schelander, Logun Schelander, Nick Greiner and daughter Lauren Greiner, three grandchildren Vivienne, Rhett, Eleanora, siblings Dena (Steve) Hart, Steven Schelander, many aunts, uncles, nieces, nephews and cousins. He is preceded in death by his parents Dennis and Karen.

A celebration of life will be in the spring.

In lieu of flowers, donations are preferred to the American Cancer Society.
